Cleaning Model

PRM_clean <- PRM %>% clean_names() %>% 
  mutate(clean_date = lubridate::ymd(sample_date)) %>% 
  select(clean_date, no3_n, k, sample_id)
Q1_clean <- Q1 %>% clean_names() %>% 
  mutate(clean_date = lubridate::ymd(sample_date)) %>% 
    select(clean_date, no3_n, k, sample_id)
Q2_clean <- Q2 %>% clean_names() %>% 
  mutate(clean_date = lubridate::ymd(sample_date)) %>% 
    select(clean_date, no3_n, k, sample_id)
Q3_clean <- Q3 %>% clean_names() %>% 
  mutate(clean_date = lubridate::ymd(sample_date)) %>% 
  select(clean_date, no3_n, k, sample_id)
